    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I'm John and I'm reaching out to you from the content department of Amazon. Amazon is known for its work culture and ensures to value employee well being. On behalf of the employee's the department has planned to organize a fun event on the upcoming Thursday, in your community centre.",
        "The event is expected to begin around 4.30 in the evening and is expected to last till dawn. We would also like to check, whether the community centre will provide us with the refreshments, as there will be around 50 attendees for the event.",
        "We were informed that the community centre makes the seating arrangement on behalf of the event organisers. So, we request you to provide enough seats that accommodate all the 50 people.",
        "On this note, we request you to block the calendar for the upcoming Thursday in the name of Amazon's content development. One of our members from the event organising committee will get in touch with the officials in the community centre, to discuss and act swiftly on the same, as the event is round the corner.",
        "Thank You,",
        "Best Regards,",
        "John"
    ],
